ople lose interest when level 20's have tacvi clickies(necro dagger) and people are scared to level past 65 because if they werent in the guilds when they initially leveled and started raiding then they are outgeared by thousands of hp/mana and get slaughtered before they can load into a zone. Besides I believe the population drop was due to WoW release....but after they realized how bad that game sucked they came back.<br><br>A fresh server, old school server at that, would revive that fun factor that is so lacking from pvp nowadays and would bring a huge responce to it and imo bring alot of people back to the game that got tired of the max resist/impossible to kill/15k hp players that are everywhere now.<br><div></div>	
