FRAUD-SZ wrote:<BR>
<DIV></DIV>***************************************************************************************<BR>We want a PvP Progression server login poll<BR><BR>Where 'we' is defined as a large percentage of the male 12-30 year old demographic, which coincidentally <SPAN><SPAN><SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></SPAN>makes up the majority of the video game market as a whole.<BR><BR>Choosing to ignore the main demographic of the entire video game industry can only be regarded as foolish at best.<BR><BR>****Kicking Snake Memorial***<BR>comment edited<BR>
